todos.title: Improve English language skills:
todos.description: Spend 30 minutes daily practicing English through reading news articles, listening to podcasts, or watching English movies.

todos.title: Stay fit and healthy:
todos.description: Engage in at least 30 minutes of moderate-intensity exercise most days of the week. This could include brisk walking, cycling, swimming, or dancing.

todos.title: Learn a new skill:
todos.description: Dedicate 1 hour each week to learning a new skill that interests you. This could be anything from coding or playing an instrument to mastering a new recipe.

todos.title: Connect with loved ones:
todos.description: Make a conscious effort to connect with friends and family more regularly. Schedule phone calls, video chats, or in-person meetings.

todos.title: Explore Mykolaiv:
todos.description: Dedicate some time each week to explore different parts of Mykolaiv. Visit local museums, historical sites, parks, or try a new restaurant.
